{"tid":384165,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港沿岸現殘體字垃圾　黃錦星堅稱整體垃圾本地為主　是港人責任","createTime":"2017-09-02T05:53:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-02T06:31:26.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b7b7d4e6e04e763c184812804f4b842c6facf825","tid":384165,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T05:53:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170902/s00001/1504319263089\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170902%2Fs00001%2F1504319263089&d=3E2S4kqCu%2B4ZpRspNF8hZhxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=95b535e8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170902%2Fs00001%2F1504319263089&h=93bc85eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170902/s00001/1504319263089</a><br />\n<br />\n環境局長黃錦星今早出席商台節目，談及香港海岸垃圾，強調大家都有責任保護環境，「（海岸垃圾）有些是區域影響，有些是本地影響。都想強調，我們自己的沿岸垃圾，整體來說，大部分是我們本地自己產生」。<br />\n<br />\n至於本港沿岸地區不時出現印上「簡體字」的垃圾，黃錦星表示，個別地區及個別風向下，「區域影響可以是大」，但整體來說香港不同海岸的垃圾，「根據過去調查，本地為本」，強調「本地人自己責任不可放輕」。<br />\n<br />\n黃錦星又提到，內地收緊進口廢料政策，對本港回收業有危有機，因為內地提高進口廢物質素，可以令回收業提高水平。他又說，因為香港生活習慣以及消費文化，減廢仍是大挑戰，要各方落實藍圖才有機會改善。"},{"pid":"2c059d3e7d2e98a85302cd6c46076494e5bedf7a","tid":384165,"uid":98584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T05:57:49.000Z","msg":"咁的確本地垃圾大部分係本地生產出嚟<br />\n唔可能話因為大陸狗垃圾就話佢地係主要生產者"},{"pid":"53ae74de30f2cbe6f7de8bc62dcddfc818186f94","tid":384165,"uid":24730,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T06:02:20.000Z","msg":"黃錦星算係本地垃圾定係支那垃圾？"},{"pid":"ee753b5d2bb205db6025e27a0f3bd57ff8326fb4","tid":384165,"uid":50740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T06:08:18.000Z","msg":"個個淘垃圾有殘體唔出奇"},{"pid":"bf3581a031c5e846bba2597a6517f77e2de7353f","tid":384165,"uid":11753,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T06:08:33.000Z","msg":"有你班垃圾執政就真係港人責任"},{"pid":"90d84b1e894cf15985258526b894f57fb883e114","tid":384165,"uid":25794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T06:14:50.000Z","msg":"D 垃圾係指港豬"},{"pid":"feccd460f01930df8297f8050c9c87900b6c494f","tid":384165,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T06:17:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>D 垃圾係指港豬</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47696dc643d5ce463b0b42849c82933367eaeb4b","tid":384165,"uid":107927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T06:31:26.000Z","msg":"港人包唔包新移民"}]}